No substitutions.

273
00:15:00,770 --> 00:15:03,390
这不是替换 是减量
This isn't a substitution. It's a reduction.

274
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:06,890
- 好吧 不准减量 - 行
- Okay.No reductions. - Fine.

275
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:08,990
