No. If we fill up on dumplings,we need to eliminate another entree.

279
00:15:14,410 --> 00:15:16,530
不准减菜
No eliminations.

280
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:19,570
多处来的就打包好了
If we have extra,we'll just take the leftovers home.

281
00:15:19,580 --> 00:15:20,400
