You're nice boys.

294
00:15:49,530 --> 00:15:51,020
告诉你我的办法
Tell you what I'm going to do.

295
00:15:51,030 --> 00:15:53,110
我给你们上四个饺子
I'm going to bring you the four dumplings.

296
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:54,990
