You go dancing every wednesday?

321
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,810
- 不 - 那就不能称跳舞之夜
No. Then that's not "dancing night."

322
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:16,290
明天陪你们玩好不好?
Look,why don't I play with you guys tomorrow?

323
00:17:16,300 --> 00:17:17,520
光晕之夜在今晚
Tonight is halo night.

324
00:17:17,530 --> 00:17:19,630
好像跟墙壁说话似的
It's like talking to a wall.

325
00:17:20,930 --> 00:17:24,210
