All right,now,sheldon,you and I are about to have a problem.

326
00:17:26,370 --> 00:17:28,610
谢尔顿 不是早都套好了台词吗?
Sheldon,remember,we role-played this.

327
00:17:28,620 --> 00:17:31,670
但是你扮的她没这么不讲理
